{{Quote|What's that?''"<br />"''It's chromastring. It'll allow a deeper penetration of some of the medications without nerve damage.|Dusque Mistflier and Finn Darktrin|<ref name="Dantooine">''[[Star Wars Galaxies: The Ruins of Dantooine]]''</ref>}}
'''Chromostring''' was a drug, patented by [[BioTech Industries/Legends|BioTech Industries]],<ref name="CRFG">[[Cracken's Rebel Field Guide (sourcebook)|''Cracken's Rebel Field Guide'']]</ref> that allowed for deeper penetration of medicines into a patient's body without causing nerve damage.<ref name="EGWT">''[[The Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref> [[Dusque Mistflier]] used chromostring to treat a wound that [[Finn Darktrin]] had suffered.<ref name="Dantooine" /> Chromostring was included in [[BioTech Industries/Legends|BioTech Industries']] [[FastFlesh medpac/Legends|FastFlesh medpac]] and was administered via a dedicated [[Chromostring Dispenser|dispenser]].<ref name="EGWT" />

